snippet.title: The official trailer for Version 1.3 [Eerie Season] is now live!
snippet.description:
Infinity Nikki Version 1.3 [Eerie Season] begins on February 25th (UTC-7)!
Get ready for:
✨ New event gameplay
✨ New dungeon
✨ New Realm Challenge
✨ Free outfit updates in [Store: Heartfelt Gifts]
...and so much more! Stylists, don't miss out on the excitement—dive in and explore!

♾️The official trailer for Version 1.3 [Eerie Season] is now live!
From the forlorn ruins, a mysterious call echoes... Within the desolate relics, ghostly whispers resound.
What hidden truth lies behind the legend?
Only the full moon knows, her haunting melody carrying the weight of her sighs...

——
